summary: This is the ninth summary report of zooplankton monitoring in the ICES Area. This year’s report includes Basin subregion, fourteen in the Baltic Sea, two in the Bay of Biscay and western Iberian Shelf, and one in the western Mediterranean Sea. This report summarizes the North Atlantic Basin and its major subregions using these 62 zooplankton monitoring sites as well as the 40 Continuous Plankton Recorder (CPR) standard areas.
title: ICES Zooplankton Status Report 2010/2011
